{"tid":1599523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟我同你講點解越嚟越少人出嚟","createTime":"2019-09-28T04:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T07:08:17.000Z","uid":126057,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e174c6743d29b2d97c39fb00d3279e5cf1b3040c","tid":1599523,"uid":126057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:35:41.000Z","msg":"係，文宣好重要，令藍轉黃好鼓舞，但呢班人本來就係自私嘅人，就算轉咗黃，九成都唔會出嚟同你行，只會立場上支持你，坐享其成。<br />\n<br />\n一場社會運動係要mobilise支持你嘅人出嚟，即係黃，再直接啲，我哋重點要係叫班<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">淺黃</span></span>嘅人再出嚟。淺黃呢個群體基數係好大，你知我知單眼佬都知，過往兩個月嘅行動好分散，但嚟緊幾日係關鍵時期，特別係<span style=\"color: gold;\">929全球反極權大遊行</span>，如果想爭取國際支持，就要顯示俾國際社會知，單單撤回係唔會令我哋撤退㗎。<br />\n<br />\n所以我喺到懇請大家：<span style=\"font-size: large;\">以往約開一齊出嚟嘅人，唔好再約，試吓主動約一啲平時story有po吓反送中嘅朋友，616有出過但之後冇出嘅朋友，總之約啲唔係深黃嘅朋友一齊出嚟行，話行完食飯又好乜都好，總之929我要見到人多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要多人到行唔撚到講撚哂粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！</span><br />\n<br />\n你諗吓如果你十五十六緊，有個frd話不如一齊去，都唔洗諗啦，親近嘅人係最能夠mobilise到人出嚟，由身邊做起，一個人越參與得多，越投入落個運動，就越維持到個參與度。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以，唔准再約上次同你一齊出嚟嘅朋友，即刻同我去約淺黃嘅朋友！！！！！！！！！</span>"},{"pid":"7074567f0c832d2170d3b90ab0837e2506ddb2e9","tid":1599523,"uid":126057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:38:34.000Z","msg":"打狗 救人"},{"pid":"0c156797ec32def2a2fc131d4e2ced312b2ff5eb","tid":1599523,"uid":126057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:38:57.000Z","msg":"打狗 救人"},{"pid":"fcf6684860accf67b1e73af3851b760b358c6b8b","tid":1599523,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7074567f0c832d2170d3b90ab0837e2506ddb2e9","tid":1599523,"uid":126057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:38:34.000Z","msg":"打狗 救人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:39:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">岳義精神 打狗救人</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3e77343df7a289f869e79f4257a2891b0733db","tid":1599523,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:57:24.000Z","msg":"唔好畀義士成為 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">condom</span></span>。"},{"pid":"4bcec5a55be671fd537a28de577ce525baef2b28","tid":1599523,"uid":126057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:07:47.000Z","msg":"打狗 救人"},{"pid":"05412aca3d0a256167a52a6e05e9ebef2f9e42ec","tid":1599523,"uid":126057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:08:17.000Z","msg":"叫埋老豆老母飲個靚茶再出嚟行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}